title: GAME OF THRONES Season 8 Episode 6 Preview Breakdown, Theories and Predictions! | Final Episode
author: Think Story
comment: Jon has basically became an extra now. he knows nothing, does nothig, just exists.

Wouldn't it be awesome if Danerys in her madness decides to kill Jon Snow with her Dragon and Arya then kills Danerys out of love of her brother then after Jon was thought be burning he walks from the fire proving to the world that he is the true Dragon King.
If Daenerys had made a beeline for Cersei and Fried her Extra Crispy, the Episode would have been EPIC!
Now watch Brienne be pregnant with Jamie's baby! 😂 oh noes.

The whole magically respawning army is what bugs me the most. Like is dany a necromancer now?? Like what was the point of the whole white walker battle showing all those dothraki lights go out and greyworm sacrificing his men if they both all just somehow came back?
